text: Fake Noise from a Box of Toys is the fourth and final studio album by American alternative rock band The Autumns, released in 2007. ==Track listing== All songs written by the Autumns. #"Turning Strangers Into Friends And Friends Into Customers" #"Boys" #"Clem" #"The Midnight Knock" #"Killer in Drag" #"Night Music" #"Only Young" #"Glass Jaw" #"Uncle Slim" #"Beautiful Boot" #"Adelaide" #"Oh My Heart" ==References== Category:2007 albums Category:The Autumns albums Category:Bella Union albums
title: Fake Noise from a Box of Toys
